                            <comment id="17885561" author="yu-lin chen" created="Sat, 28 Sep 2024 11:22:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The first issue, &quot;Unexpected state transition from ERROR to PENDING_SHUTDOWN&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, was caused by a racing between streams.close() and shutdownHelper() thread &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After GlobalThread dead, the shutdownHelper() thread is triggered asynchronously. &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
The state of KafkaStream&#160;changes in this order: RUNNING -&amp;gt; PENDING_ERROR -&amp;gt; ERROR&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, the test called stream.close() in parallel &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, which conduct a non-atomic check-and-set flow as shown below: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;5&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;state.hasCompletedShutdown() (Passed if state is in PENDING_ERROR)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;state.isShuttingDown() (Passed if state is in ERROR)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;setState(State.PENDING_SHUTDOWN)&#160;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The third step will throw an error since state transition &quot;ERROR to PENDING_SHUTDOWN&quot; is illegal.&lt;br/&gt;
This racing issue can be simulated by the attached patch. &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13071847/13071847_0001-reproduce-unexpected-state-transition.patch&quot; title=&quot;0001-reproduce-unexpected-state-transition.patch attached to KAFKA-17646&quot;&gt;0001-reproduce-unexpected-state-transition.patch&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L343&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L343&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L696&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L696&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L1590&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L1590&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreamsTest.java#L550C1-L551C1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreamsTest.java#L550C1-L551C1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;5&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L1546-L1565&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreams.java#L1546-L1565&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17885563" author="yu-lin chen" created="Sat, 28 Sep 2024 11:58:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The second issue, &quot;Condition not met within timeout 15000&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, occured when the KafkaStreams stayed in &quot;PENDING_ERROR&quot; for too short time . In my local PC, it only stay for 7 ms before transite to ERROR.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This can be reproduced by adding a little delay before checking &quot;PENDING_ERROR&quot; in the test:&#160; patch &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13071848/13071848_0002-reproduce-waiting-timeout-for-PENDING_ERROR.patch&quot; title=&quot;0002-reproduce-waiting-timeout-for-PENDING_ERROR.patch attached to KAFKA-17646&quot;&gt;0002-reproduce-waiting-timeout-for-PENDING_ERROR.patch&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreamsTest.java#L547&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/blob/1854d4b8a11461b53b59fa109b95f2a4f5003997/streams/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/KafkaStreamsTest.java#L547&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
